            <p>Mechanics, Forces, Energy, Work, Kinematics (movements), Electricity, Magnetism, Calorimetry (heat), Optics, Lenses, Waves, etc</p>

            <h6><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success"></i> SNT & NSI (computer science)</h6>
            <p>Programming, Python, Algorithmics, Data structures, Trees, Graphs, Databases, SQL, etc</p>
          </div>
        </div>
