        <div class="row">
          <p class="lead text-justify col-lg-9">Hello! I'm Authmane Terki, I live in Switzerland, more precisely in Lausanne. Freelance online tutor, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/authmane-terki-full-stack-developer/" target="_blank">ex developer</a>, founder of Mathcam a Swiss company in online tutoring, I offer lessons in math, physics and chemistry, mainly for the levels &quot;collège&quot; and &quot;lycée&quot; of the French and Swiss education systems.<br /><br />After several years of experience, I have been able to bring together many very valuable tips, techniques and resources, old exams and awesome exercises.<br /><br />The satisfaction of the many students I have supported - many of whom have passed their exams - fuels my interest in teaching, while I have been passionate about math and physics since my younger age and <a href="/attestations-{{lang}}.html" class="d-inline">qualified 3 times for the Swiss final of the International Mathematical and Logic Games Championship.</a></p>
